#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.45:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga"
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Puññābhisandasutta"
msgstr "45. Overflowing Merit"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā sovaggikā "
"sukhavipākā saggasaṃvattanikā iṭṭhāya kantāya manāpāya hitāya sukhāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these five kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing "
"goodness. They nurture happiness and are conducive to heaven, ripening in "
"happiness and leading to heaven. They lead to what is likable, desirable, "
"agreeable, to welfare and happiness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:2.1"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.45:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cīvaraṃ paribhuñjamāno appamāṇaṃ cetosamādhiṃ "
"upasampajja viharati, appamāṇo tassa puññābhisando kusalābhisando "
"sukhassāhāro sovaggiko sukhavipāko saggasaṃvattaniko iṭṭhāya kantāya "
"manāpāya hitāya sukhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant enters and remains in a limitless immersion of heart while "
"using a robe …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhu piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñjamāno … pe … yassa, bhikkhave, "
"bhikkhu vihāraṃ paribhuñjamāno … pe … yassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mañcapīṭhaṃ "
"paribhuñjamāno … pe …."
msgstr "alms-food … lodging … bed and chair …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.52"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhu gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paribhuñjamāno "
"appamāṇaṃ cetosamādhiṃ upasampajja viharati, appamāṇo tassa puññābhisando "
"kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro sovaggiko sukhavipāko saggasaṃvattaniko iṭṭhāya "
"kantāya manāpāya hitāya sukhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"medicines and supplies for the sick, the overflowing of merit for the donor "
"is limitless …"

msgctxt "an5.45:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā "
"sovaggikā sukhavipākā saggasaṃvattanikā iṭṭhāya kantāya manāpāya hitāya "
"sukhāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"These are the five kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness. They "
"nurture happiness, and are conducive to heaven, ripening in happiness, and "
"leading to heaven. They lead to what is likable, desirable, agreeable, to "
"welfare and happiness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:5.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi ca pana, bhikkhave, pañcahi puññābhisandehi kusalābhisandehi "
"samannāgatassa ariyasāvakassa na sukaraṃ puññassa pamāṇaṃ gahetuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When a noble disciple has these five kinds of overflowing merit and "
"goodness, it’s not easy to grasp how much merit they have by saying that"

msgctxt "an5.45:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘ettako puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro sovaggiko sukhavipāko "
"saggasaṃvattaniko iṭṭhāya kantāya manāpāya hitāya sukhāya saṃvattatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"this is the extent of their overflowing merit … that leads to happiness."

msgctxt "an5.45:5.3"
msgid "Atha kho asaṅkheyyo appameyyo mahāpuññakkhandhotveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"It’s simply reckoned as an incalculable, immeasurable, great mass of merit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:6.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāsamudde na sukaraṃ udakassa pamāṇaṃ gahetuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"It’s like trying to grasp how much water is in the ocean. It’s not easy to "
"say:"

msgctxt "an5.45:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘ettakāni udakāḷhakānīti vā ettakāni udakāḷhakasatānīti vā ettakāni "
"udakāḷhakasahassānīti vā ettakāni udakāḷhakasatasahassānīti vā;"
msgstr ""
"‘This is how many gallons, how many hundreds, thousands, hundreds of "
"thousands of gallons there are.’"

msgctxt "an5.45:6.3"
msgid "atha kho asaṅkheyyo appameyyo mahāudakakkhandhotveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati’."
msgstr ""
"It’s simply reckoned as an incalculable, immeasurable, great mass of water."

msgctxt "an5.45:6.4"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, imehi pañcahi puññābhisandehi kusalābhisandehi "
"samannāgatassa ariyasāvakassa na sukaraṃ puññassa pamāṇaṃ gahetuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when a noble disciple has these five kinds of overflowing "
"merit and goodness, it’s not easy to grasp how much merit they have:"

msgctxt "an5.45:6.5"
msgid ""
"‘ettako puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro sovaggiko sukhavipāko "
"saggasaṃvattaniko iṭṭhāya kantāya manāpāya hitāya sukhāya saṃvattatī’ti."
msgstr "‘This is how much this overflowing merit … leads to happiness.’"

msgctxt "an5.45:6.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho asaṅkheyyo appameyyo mahāpuññakkhandhotveva saṅkhaṃ gacchatīti."
msgstr ""
"It’s simply reckoned as an incalculable, immeasurable, great mass of merit."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:7.1"
msgid "Mahodadhiṃ aparimitaṃ mahāsaraṃ,"
msgstr "Hosts of people use the rivers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.45:7.2"
msgid "Bahubheravaṃ ratnagaṇānamālayaṃ;"
msgstr "and though the rivers are many,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: naragaṇasaṅghasevitā → macchagaṇasaṃghasevitā (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.45:7.3"
msgid "Najjo yathā naragaṇasaṅghasevitā,"
msgstr "all reach the great deep, the boundless ocean,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.45:7.4"
msgid "Puthū savantī upayanti sāgaraṃ."
msgstr "the cruel sea that’s home to precious gems."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.53"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.45:8.1"
msgid "Evaṃ naraṃ annadapānavatthadaṃ,"
msgstr "So too, when a person gives food, drink, and clothes;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.45:8.2"
msgid "Seyyānisajjattharaṇassa dāyakaṃ;"
msgstr "and they’re a giver of beds, seats, and mats—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.45:8.3"
msgid "Puññassa dhārā upayanti paṇḍitaṃ,"
msgstr "the streams of merit reach that astute person,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.45:8.4"
msgid "Najjo yathā vārivahāva sāgaran”ti."
msgstr "as the rivers bring their waters to the sea.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.45:8.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
